Some have come in puppy love
perchance to steal a kiss

22
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:24,949
Some are still enamoured
after years of wedded bliss

23
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:28,157
Everyone's parading
down the promenade in pairs

24
